# Cosmos modernization checklist

Jackal is migrating from SDK 0.45 to the **2026.1** stack (SDK **0.54.x**, CometBFT 0.39, ibc-go v11, wasmd 0.70). There is no SDK 0.55 release yet.

## Required on every migration PR

1. Read [docs/COSMOS-MODERNIZATION.md](docs/COSMOS-MODERNIZATION.md) for the active phase and unchecked items.
2. After completing work, update that file:
   - Check off finished checklist items (`[x]`).
   - Bump **Last updated** date.
   - Append a row to **Phase log** (date, phase, short note).
   - Update version matrix if `go.mod` pins changed.
3. Do not skip phases (0.47 → 0.50 → 0.53 → 0.54). Each hop needs an on-chain upgrade (`v600`, `v610`, …).
4. Re-port Jackal-specific patches in-app (e.g. `app/ante_fee.go`), not via SDK forks.
5. Diff `app/app.go` against the **wasmd template** for the target SDK version.

## Phase 1 (`v600`) branch reminders

- Upgrade handler: `app/upgrades/v600/`
- Free storage fees: `app/ante_fee.go`
- Proto codegen must use `cosmos/gogoproto`; run `make proto-gen` on Linux when touching `.proto` files.
